    End If
    Return 1
End Process

Note: ============================================================
Note: HIR_INCREASE_STATEMENT post handler (11021)
Note: ============================================================

@Reasoning
HIR_INCREASE_STATEMENT post: "Increase X by N" — equivalent to
X = X + N. The visitor pushes the target address (child 0) and
the increase amount (child 1). Identical shape to compound assign
with operator hard-coded to MIR_ADD (20002).
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
1. Pop amount (child 1) and target (child 0).
2. Emit load + add + store with MIR_ADD opcode.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Three instruction emissions per Increase.
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Null target or amount is a lowering error.
@End Security_Scope

